Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Base
      • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.BaseResource
        • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Resource
          • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.DomainResource
            • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Group
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IAnyResource, IBase, IBaseHasExtensions, IBaseHasModifierExtensions, IBaseResource, IDomainResource

    public class Group
extends DomainResource
    Represents a defined collection of entities that may be discussed or acted upon collectively but which are not expected to act collectively and are not formally or legally recognized. I.e. A collection of entities that isn't an Organization.
